Rating: 3
I used herbs de provence that a friend picked up recently while in Provence. I used a 5 lb chicken and sprinkled 1 tsp in the cavity. I also sprinkled the herbs liberally on the outside after I massaged with the butter. Did the carrot and onion and the sauce. Cooked in the convection oven at 400 for the first 15 mins, and 325 for the remaining 1 hr and 45 mins. Two thumbs up.

