Rating: 3
I absolutely loved this sauce, although I did not follow the recipe exactly. I used chicken broth and I didn't use the roasting pan to simmer the sauce. I poured the juices from the pan directly into a saucepan and then followed the rest of the recipe. It wasn't very thick, but it tasted great, especially good for dipping bread into!! YUM